('Information about Connection Gateways and Low Latency Connections:\r\n\r\nwhen you execute gwconnect for low latency gateway\r\nyou send the request to connect gateway\r\nso in your gwconnect script you should give connGateway host and port\r\nConnGateway internally identifies everytime a low latency gateway starts up in the environment\r\nsince Gateway-05 was set as a low latency gateway it joined the connGateway pool as soon as it was restarted\r\nwe only need to send request to ConnGateway, it will then decide out of its pool of Gateway which one to pick \r\n\r\nIn TC-OAT:\r\n/home/gtsman/scripts/sqmRotate/gwconnect.py -h tc-oat02 -p 20050 --LLO -s 60 -u WLV01M-4\r\n\r\nIn OpCon:\r\n/Hosts/tcoat01/Gateway-5_051> show GWConfiguration\r\n...\r\n<clientListenPort value=\\"20051\\"/>\r\n...\r\n<externalInterface value=\\"51.3.62.51\\"/>\r\n<bindToExternalInterface value=\\"TRUE\\"/>\r\n\r\nIn OpCon:\r\n/Hosts/tcoat02/ConnGateway-1_051> show StartupParams\r\n...\r\n<vector value=\\"--connectionGateway\\"/>\r\n...\r\n\r\n/Hosts/tcoat02/ConnGateway-1_051> show GWConfiguration\r\n<clientListenPort value=\\"20050\\"/>\r\n...', '2013-12-19 13:56:37', 23),
('Sample --\r\nThe inner SELECT uses an OUTER JOIN to join the orderclearingrelation table with the orderbook table for all entries where the exchange order ids and product ids are equal.  Because itâ€™s a LEFT OUTER JOIN, all the entries from the orderclearingrelation table will be present whether or not there is a match in the orderbook table.  For rows where there is no match, all of the orderbook table columns will be NULL.  \r\n\r\nSo, we want to find all of the cases where this is not match in the orderbook table.  This is what the â€œob.productid IS NULLâ€ clause is checking for.\r\n\r\nThe query then uses the results of the inner SELECT as a table in the outer query (either SELECT or DELETE).\r\n\r\nSELECT ocr.exchangeorderid,ocr.productid,ocr.position\r\nFROM obsdb21.orderclearingrelation ocr,\r\n     (SELECT ocr1.exchangeorderid,ocr1.productid\r\n      FROM obsdb21.orderclearingrelation ocr1\r\n           LEFT OUTER JOIN obsdb21.orderbook ob\r\n           ON ocr1.exchangeorderid = ob.exchangeorderid AND ocr1.productid = ob.productid\r\n      WHERE ob.productid IS NULL\r\n      GROUP BY ocr1.exchangeorderid,ocr1.productid) AS invalid_ocr\r\nWHERE ocr.exchangeorderid = invalid_ocr.exchangeorderid AND ocr.productid = invalid_ocr.productid\r\n\r\nDELETE ocr\r\nFROM obsdb21.orderclearingrelation ocr,\r\n     (SELECT ocr1.exchangeorderid,ocr1.productid\r\n      FROM obsdb21.orderclearingrelation ocr1\r\n           LEFT OUTER JOIN obsdb21.orderbook ob\r\n           ON ocr1.exchangeorderid = ob.exchangeorderid AND ocr1.productid = ob.productid\r\n      WHERE ob.productid IS NULL\r\n      GROUP BY ocr1.exchangeorderid,ocr1.productid) AS invalid_ocr\r\nWHERE ocr.exchangeorderid = invalid_ocr.exchangeorderid AND ocr.productid = invalid_ocr.productid\r\n\r\n', '2013-12-19 16:35:11', 24),
