2014_01_06_cleanorderbook_ISE_AllPartitions.o\r\n\r\nCleanup run on ISE partitions 1,2,3:\r\nâ€¢	./cleanOrderbook.py -m ISE -p 1 -p 2 -p 3 -v -d > /tmp/2014_01_06_cleanorderbook_ISE_p1_p2_p3.o\r\n\r\nCleanup run on ISE partitions 4,5,6 and Gemini partitions 51, 52, 53\r\nâ€¢	./cleanOrderbook.py -m ISE -m GEMINI -p 1 -p 2 -p 3 -p 51 -p 52 -p 53 -v -d > /tmp/2014_01_06_cleanorderbook_ISE_GEMINI_p1_p2_p3_p51_p52_p53.o\r\n', '2014-01-09 10:46:12', 44),
